list.name: Default
list.comment: changes for new typedefs removed warnings Mask moved to Base lib flags reworked: - each entity has two sets of flags - double buffer fashion - when flag is "Resolved": -- flag bit is moved from next_flags to curr_flags, and zeroed in curr_flags -- also entity is added to FlaggedSystems, which is new type of system that updates only flagged entities -- its entity list is cleared each frame added simple profiling of systems

Added EntityBase, which now contains roles mask, all Entity types must derive from it defered entity destruction (dying flag)
